@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1
@adminToken = replace-with-admin-access-token
@studentToken = replace-with-student-access-token

### Portal home aggregation
GET {{baseUrl}}/portal/home

### Current user as anonymous
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me

### CAS login URL
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/cas/login-url?redirectUri=http://localhost:5173/callback

### CAS callback with mock ticket
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/cas/callback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ticket": "replace-with-mock-ticket",
  "service": "http://localhost:5173/callback"
}

### Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}

### List public courses
GET {{baseUrl}}/portal/courses?page=1&size=10&keyword=math

### Get course detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/portal/courses/replace-with-course-id

### Launch course
POST {{baseUrl}}/portal/courses/replace-with-course-id/launch
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Admin list CMS articles
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/articles?page=1&size=10&status=DRAFT
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Admin create CMS draft
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/articles
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test Article",
  "summary": "Created by QA HTTP example.",
  "content": "Draft content for API validation.",
  "status": "DRAFT",
  "categoryId": 1
}

### Admin publish CMS article (designed endpoint, may be blocked until implemented)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/articles/replace-with-article-id/publish
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Admin create course sync job (designed endpoint, may be blocked until implemented)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/course-sync/jobs
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "syncType": "COURSE_CATALOG",
  "mode": "INCREMENTAL",
  "termCode": "2026-SPRING"
}

### Admin get sync job status
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/course-sync/jobs/replace-with-job-id
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
